-0\n      tw-m-0\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \n      tw-duration-500 \n      tw-ease-in-out \n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003eedit.php?post_type=wpdmpro\u0026amp;page=wpdm-stats\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"/2025-10-06-cve-2025-10146/debug.png\"\n    alt=\"Breakpoint debugging to observe GET params\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n      \u003cp\u003eBreakpoint debugging to observe GET params\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTrước tiên, plugin lấy toàn bộ \u003cstrong\u003eGET parameters\u003c/strong\u003e vào \u003ccode\u003e$get_params\u003c/code\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNếu \u003ccode\u003e$user_ids\u003c/code\u003e không rỗng, plugin sẽ tạo \u003cstrong\u003enút “Clear filter”\u003c/strong\u003e. Để làm nút này hoạt động, cần một URL mà \u003cstrong\u003ekhông còn \u003ccode\u003euser_ids\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e nữa, nên plugin làm như sau:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n        tw-mx-2 \n        tw-flex\n        tw-flex-row\n        tw-flex-1\"\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.co