8 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/button\u003e\n        \n      \u003cbutton \n        class=\"\n          tw-select-none \n          tw-mx-2 \n          tw-block \n          group-[.is-open]:tw-hidden \n          print:!tw-hidden\" \n        disabled\n        aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M328 256c0 39.8-32.2 72-72 72s-72-32.2-72-72 32.2-72 72-72 72 32.2 72 72zm104-72c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72zm-352 0c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \n    id=\"codeblock-id-72\" \n    class=\"\n      chroma \n      !tw-block \n      tw-p-0\n      tw-m-0\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \n      tw-duration-500 \n      tw-ease-in-out \n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e[demo_wp_query]\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e👉 Truy vấn sẽ được hiển thị khi truy cập \u003ccode\u003ehttp://localhost/\u0026lt;page-title\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/demo_page.png\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n      \u003ch4\u003eTrang demo hiển thị kết quả WP_Query\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"analysis\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#analysis\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e73 Analysis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ewpdb\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLà lớp PHP cốt lõi của WordPress dùng để thao tác trực tiếp với MySQL.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCho phép lập trình viên \u003cstrong\u003eviết và thực thi câu SQL thô\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWP_Query\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLà một lớp trừu tượng hóa giúp lấy dữ liệu bài viết (post) từ database mà \u003cstrong\u003ekhông cần viết SQL trực tiếp\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLập trình viên chỉ cần truyền vào mảng tham số (args), WordPress sẽ tự động dựng câu SQL phù hợp.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMối quan hệ\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eWP_Query không trực tiếp truy vấn MySQL.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThay vào đó, nó xây dựng câu SQL dựa trên args, áp dụng các bước \u003cstrong\u003ekiểm tra\u003c/strong\u003e/\u003cstrong\u003evalidate\u003c/strong\u003e, rồi gọi \u003ccode\u003e$wpdb\u003c/code\u003e để thực thi.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"patch-diff\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#patch-diff\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e73.1 Patch Diff\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eWordPress là một dự án \u003cstrong\u003emã nguồn mở\u003c/strong\u003e với kho lưu trữ được công khai trên \u003cstrong\u003eGitHub\u003c/strong\u003e. Vì vậy, mọi bản vá đều được commit trực tiếp tại đây. Do đó, để phân tích một lỗ hổng, ta chỉ cần tìm đến commit liên quan và quan sát sự thay đổi trong mã nguồn.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTrong phần reference của \u003cstrong\u003eCVE-2022-21661\u003c/strong\u003e, có liên kết đến \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/wordpress-develop/commit/17efac8c8ec64555eff5cf51a3eff81e06317214\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003ecommit\u003c/a\u003e trên GitHub:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/patch_diff.png\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n      \u003ch4\u003eSo sánh bản vá giữa hai phiên bản\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eLỗ hổng được vá trong file \u003cstrong\u003esrc/wp-includes/class-wp-tax-query.php\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBản lỗi\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n        tw-mx-2 \n        tw-flex\n        tw-flex-row\n        tw-flex-1\"\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cp class=\"tw-select-none !tw-my-1\"\u003ephp\u003c/p\u003e\n      \u003c/button\u003e\n\n   \u003cdiv class=\"tw-flex\"\u003e\n      \u003cbutton \n        class=\"\n          line-number-button\n          tw-mx-2 \n          tw-hidden \n          grou