m\"\u003e1.1\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTa tách mệnh đề \u003ccode\u003eORDER BY\u003c/code\u003e bằng \u003ccode\u003e,\u003c/code\u003e vì nó chấp nhập \u003cstrong\u003emulti column\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"/2025-09-21-cve-2025-39566/time_response.png\"\n    alt=\"time response\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n      \u003cp\u003eTime response\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eKết quả: thời gian phản hồi bị delay =\u0026gt; SQL Injection thành công.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"dump-data-from-database\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#dump-data-from-database\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e12.4 Dump Data from Database\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBypass \u003ccode\u003e'\u003c/code\u003e using ORD()\u003c/strong\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eĐể dump dữ liệu của database ta cần thử để lấy ký tự đầu tiên của \u003cstrong\u003edatabase name\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDo \u003ccode\u003esanitize_text_field()\u003c/code\u003e loại bỏ \u003ccode\u003e'\u003c/code\u003e, ta không dùng được payload so sánh trực tiếp. Thay vào đó dùng \u003ccode\u003eORD()\u003c/code\u003e để so sánh ký tự theo ASCII:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n        tw-mx-2 \n        tw-flex\n        tw-flex-row\n        tw-flex-1\"\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    x